//Journal:Having trouble keeping track of your quests? You could write them down if only you had something to write in.
DefiledSpikes: Are the spikes the Defiled Wastelands uses for nightmares bigger than itself in your way? Some bombs and rope can help!
Assimilation: The cure to assimilation? The Dryad is your gal.
CursedItems: Curses are fun and all, but you can neutralize the world of evil by breaking curses at a Bewitching Table!
EvilWeaknesses: Eaters cast a dark shadow when burnt bright, gorey abominations wither from poisonous injections, chunky antibodies shatter from a real shock and gooey friends can't eat when it gets cold. Give the world's evils a surprise...
StoneMask: Somewhere along the surface of the world awaits the crown of a once beloved jester...
RivenWater: Those pools in the Hives of the Riven would make for excellent hot tubs if they didn't digest you. What a shame.
